---
import LegalLayout from '../components/LegalLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';

// TODO(client): have counsel review before launch (see README pre-launch list).
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Reliant Construction"
  description="How Reliant Construction collects, uses, and protects your information when you visit our site or request an estimate."
  heading="Privacy policy"
  effective="July 12, 2026"
>
  <p>
    This policy describes how {site.legalName} ("Reliant Construction," "we," "us") collects,
    uses, and protects information when you visit {site.url.replace('https://', '')} or contact
    us about a project. The short version: we collect what we need to respond to your inquiry
    and run our business, we never sell your information, and we don't add you to marketing
    lists you didn't ask for.
  </p>

  <div>
    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p class="mt-3">When you submit an estimate or contact form, we collect the details you provide:</p>
    <ul class="mt-3">
      <li>Name, phone number, and email address</li>
      <li>Project location (town and state) and project type</li>
      <li>Anything you write in the project description</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-3">
      Like most websites, our hosting provider may also log standard technical data (IP
      address, browser type, pages visited) for security and performance purposes.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2>How we use it</h2>
    <ul class="mt-3">
      <li>To respond to your inquiry, schedule walkthroughs, and prepare proposals</li>
      <li>To communicate about an active or prospective project</li>
      <li>To maintain business records we're required to keep</li>
      <li>To improve our website and services</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2>What we don't do</h2>
    <ul class="mt-3">
      <li>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information</li>
      <li>We do not add you to marketing lists without your consent</li>
      <li>We do not share your information except as described below</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2>Service providers</h2>
    <p class="mt-3">
      We use trusted third-party services to operate this site — including form processing and
      website hosting. These providers process your information on our behalf, only as needed
      to deliver their service, and are not permitted to use it for their own purposes. We may
      also disclose information when required by law.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2>Our sister company</h2>
    <p class="mt-3">
      If your inquiry involves solar work, we may share relevant project details with our
      sister company, Reliant Solar, so one team can coordinate your project. The same
      no-selling, no-marketing-lists commitments apply.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2>Data retention</h2>
    <p class="mt-3">
      We keep inquiry and project records for as long as needed to serve you and to meet
      legal, warranty, and insurance obligations — construction records often must be
      retained for the duration of applicable warranty periods.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2>Your choices</h2>
    <p class="mt-3">
      You can ask us to access, correct, or delete the personal information we hold about you
      (subject to records we're legally required to keep). Contact us at
      <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`} class="font-semibold text-brand-deep hover:underline">{site.email}</a>
      or {site.phoneDisplay} and we'll respond within a reasonable time.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
    <p class="mt-3">
      Our services are for property owners and businesses. We do not knowingly collect
      information from children under 13.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p class="mt-3">
      If we update this policy, we'll post the new version here with a new effective date.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p class="mt-3">
      {site.legalName}<br />
      {site.address.street}, {site.address.city}, {site.address.region} {site.address.zip}<br />
      <a href={site.phoneHref} class="font-semibold text-brand-deep hover:underline">{site.phoneDisplay}</a> ·
      <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`} class="font-semibold text-brand-deep hover:underline">{site.email}</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</LegalLayout>
